query:
insert into underway.activity_call (
                    id,
                    task_queue_name,
                    workflow_run_id,
                    step_index,
                    call_key,
                    activity,
                    input,
                    state
                ) values ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, 'pending'::underway.activity_call_state)
                on conflict (task_queue_name, workflow_run_id, step_index, call_key) do nothing
